DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-2.939ft at 12:06\n-0.036ft at 15:06\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Easing\, modest scale mix of SSW swell and NW swell for surf mainly runnin
 g thigh to waist high. Tide sensitive breaks bogged down by mid morning hi
 gh tide. Ebbing\, early afternoon tide likely most favorable.\n\nMorning w
 inds look light\, then light+ SW onshore due for the afternoon. 
END:VEVENT
