BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260331T070000
DTEND:20260331T073000
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-2.499ft at 07:00\n-2.999ft at 07:30\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Morning starts off small with meager swell and a 5'+ mid AM high tide.  Wa
 ves getting thigh-stomach high zone over the afternoon as fresh mix of WNW
  swell and shorter-period SSW windswell rolls in. Nice incoming tide push 
 later afternoon/evening. \n\nConditions looking a little sketchy at this p
 oint\, with SSW winds due through the day\, light+ in the morning then ris
 ing to moderate during the afternoon.
END:VEVENT
