BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260401T065400
DTEND:20260401T083000
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-1.384ft at 06:54\n-2.964ft at 08:30\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Modest scale mix of peaking WNW swell and lingering SSW swell looks good f
 or waist-stomach-chest high surf in the morning\, followed by slow fading 
 waves over the afternoon. \n\nNice tide push early morning\, then tide sen
 sitive spots get bogged down by later morning high tide. Offshore NW winds
  due all day\, light in the morning then moderate for the afternoon. 
END:VEVENT
